    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter to complain about some trade which were mistakenly stated in my June 2022 credit card statement.",
        "I am J A T S Perera who holds the NIC number 905190113V and the credit card number 5556678",
        "at your bank. I have been using your credit card facility since year 2014 and I am maintaining a better relationship with the bank for the past 6 years. Hence, your bank has extended my credit limit last year to Rs. 400,000/=.",
        "I received my credit card statement yesterday which consisted with three irrelevant transactions from 20th June 2022 to 25th June 2022. During the mentioned period, I have not used my credit card for any sort of purchases. Moreover, I am not utilizing this credit card to purchase electrical items because I have a seperate card to carry out such transactions.",
